jobInfo.postDescription:
Start or continue your international career with this excellent opportunity to join the world’s leading forwarding and logistics organisation and be part of our ongoing success story.
As a member of the regional software development team, you will offer a diverse range of solutions to cater the needs of various business units in Asia Pacific region. 


Your tasks and responsibilities:

•	Analyse requirements and design business solutions for Asia Pacific and corporate functional / business units in accordance with organization's information system architecture
•	Develop / modify software and support the solutions after implementation
•	Explore and implement new software technology to serve business solutions
•	Design, develop, maintain and support enterprise scale applications designed with multi-layer architecture


Your skills and experience:

•	Higher Diploma or Degree Holder in Computer Science or equivalent
•	1-4 years' hands-on experience
•	Well versed with development on open source frameworks with Java, e.g. Spring, Hibernate, jQuery, Maven, Gradle, etc.Knowledge and experience in Javascript, React, Angular and/or other web development toolkits
•	Experience in RDMS such as Oracle, MySQL, PostgreSQL and MSSQLExperience with container technologies like Openshift and/or Docker as well would be considered as a big plus
•	Knowledge in mobile app (Swift / Objective-C for iOS, Flutter / Dart for Android, Ionic / React Native) development is a plus but not necessary 
•	Good command of both verbal and written English


Good reasons to join

At Kuehne + Nagel, you get to grow your expertise, shape processes and deliver innovative solutions. We are continuously building our local and global network and our product portfolio, creating career opportunities in different fields of work worldwide. As a leader in the logistics industry, we provide a collaborative and IT driven environment where you will work with motivated and customer-centric colleagues across the world.
jobInfo.address: 上海静安区市北壹中心1号楼

brandComInfo.introduce:
德迅集团是全球首屈一指的物流服务公司，拥有超过125年的历史，业务遍及100多个国家1,300个地点，共聘用超过76,000名员工。 德迅主要业务涵盖海、陆、空运和合约式物流服务，并提供以资讯科技为本的供应链管理方案。
在中国市场拥有超过45年的稳固基础,早于1965年在亚洲香港成立首家办事处。1979年在北京成立首家办事处，成为首批涉足中国大陆地区的国际物流服务供应商之一。
德迅为所有主要行业提供量身定造的物流方案。
       首家获得“甲级货运代理牌照“的全外资物流企业。 
       德迅中国公司分布于全国38个城市，员工人数超过3,000人，来自世界18个国家。
